= F 0
= T 1

= Y 1
= N 0

= (toBool x)    | 2 F _&T x
= (not x)       | 2 T _&F x
= (if x t e)    | 2 e _&t x
= (ifNot x t e) | 2 t _&e x

= (and x y)  | if x (toBool y) F
= (or x y)   | if x T (toBool y)
= (xor x y)  | if x (not y) (toBool y)
= (nand x y) | not (and x y)
= (nor x y)  | not (or x y)
= (xnor x y) | not (xor x y)
